Notice: Only support linux platform.

Dependency:
    * python >= 2.6

for html, php ... Extract Regrex
        (r'<script type=[\'"]?text/javascript[\'"]?>.*?</script>', re.M|re.S)

Install:
    No need to make; make install; Just copy to some folder, that's all

How to use:
    see ./hint.py --help
    
FINISH:
    v8 engine add
    plugin support
    --plugin --config support
